<div align="left"><p>You are receiving this email because you have subscribed to receive email notifications for Cephos LLC - 20261676445.</p>
<p>Helpful tip: If you haven&#8217;t already done so, you may want to add a general business email address that would be accessible to more than one employee. This will help keep important information and notices from being overlooked.</p>
<p>Notifications are a courtesy reminder. You are responsible for tracking and filing timely updates for your entity and being aware of filing requirements. Make sure that you save our email address so these notices aren&#8217;t delivered to your spam folder.</p>
<p>Not receiving our notice for any reason does not excuse filing requirements for this entity.</p>
<p>For additional information, see our <a href="https://coloradosos.gov/pubs/business/FAQs/email.html">email notification FAQs</a>.</p>
<p>&#160;</p>
<p>This is an automatically generated email. If you would like to contact our office, please send an email to <a href="mailto:business@coloradosos.gov">business@coloradosos.gov</a> or call 303-894-2200 and press 2.</p>
<p>If you would like to unsubscribe from this email notification service, visit our website, <a href="https://coloradosos.gov/">coloradosos.gov</a>, select "Business Organizations" in the menu on the left, then click on "Email Notifications".</p><br />
